":"Answer","text":"Yes. Multi-location practices can create dedicated pages for each site, complete with address, working hours, contact details, and maps."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I publish health content for patients?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. The website includes a blog and content pages where you can share articles, treatment information, and educational resources — helping position your practice as a trusted source."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do I need a developer to update the website?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. Content management is built in. You can update pages, add new services, and publish articles instantly without technical help."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8"><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Do I need a separate website if I already use the Virtual Practice?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">Do I need a separate website if I already use the Virtual Practice?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Can patients book appointments directly on the website?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">Can patients book appointments directly on the website?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Is the website mobile-friendly?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justif